    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "c2c306d5-077d-4cf2-aea1-0622c643558a",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Devil&apos;s Wingman III - Props to you Both",
        "Location": "LOCATION_GOLDEN_GECKO",
        "PublicId": "127824306838",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/golden/mission_gecko/scene_gecko_basic.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 1e0f5eed-8cfd-4b85-9593-38df4c7ce490).Image",
        "Description": "Thanks to you, 47, our client and his online dating service match are now boo’d up. He wants to make her Christmas special, and a silver letter opener from the Burj Al-Ghazali where the two vacationed (on her dime) is a perfect gift. Moreover, a romantic helicopter tour of Martha’s Vineyard will be an exciting holiday adventure. Assuming our client is the pilot he claims to be, the only thing missing is the chopper. Both you and your client will receive props on the completion of this operation.",
